        "Description": "Good evening, 47\r\rStephen Burns, a rogue scientist whose twisted experiments have caught the attention of the world&apos;s most secretive and powerful organizations. Burns has developed a lethal concoction, which we&apos;ve codenamed &quot;Clown&apos;s Grin.&quot; This insidious poison drives its victims into a frenzied dance until their bodies can no longer sustain the torment, leading to a gruesome death. \r\rYour mission;  eliminate Burns by injectining him with his own poison, delivering a fitting end.\r\rGood Luck 47",
